# SSH Script Runner — Project Overview

Full-stack application for managing and executing compliance checks on remote hosts via SSH/WinRM. Includes project-based execution workflow, RBAC, scheduling, IS catalog, IB security profiles, and offline mode.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Backend | FastAPI 0.110 (Python 3.11), Uvicorn |
| Database | MongoDB 6.0 via Motor (async) |
| Frontend | React 19, React Router 7, Tailwind CSS, Radix UI (shadcn/ui) |
| Auth | JWT (access + refresh tokens), bcrypt, Fernet encryption |
| Real-time | Server-Sent Events (SSE) |
| Remote exec | Paramiko (SSH), pywinrm (WinRM) |
| Build | Docker, Docker Compose (dev / prod / offline), nginx |
| Testing | pytest (backend), React Testing Library + MSW (frontend) |

## Entry Points

| Entry | Path | Details |
|-------|------|---------|
| Backend server | `backend/server.py` | FastAPI app, startup: DB indexes, admin user, default roles, scheduler |
| Frontend app | `frontend/src/index.js` → `App.js` | React root, BrowserRouter, lazy-loaded routes |
| API root | `/api` | All backend endpoints under this prefix |
| Health check | `GET /api/health` | Returns DB status |

## Main Components

| Component | Location | Purpose |
|-----------|----------|---------|
| API layer | `backend/api/` | 15 route modules (auth, hosts, projects, executions, etc.) |
| Services | `backend/services/` | Business logic (execution, scheduler, offline, IB apply) |
| Models | `backend/models/` | Pydantic models for all domain entities |
| Config | `backend/config/` | Settings, DB, security, rate limiting |
| Pages | `frontend/src/pages/` | 17+ page components with lazy loading |
| UI kit | `frontend/src/components/ui/` | 50+ shadcn/ui components, MD3 theme layer |
| Hooks | `frontend/src/hooks/` | useApiLoader, usePermissions, useDialog, etc. |
| Auth context | `frontend/src/contexts/AuthContext.js` | Global auth state, permissions |
| API client | `frontend/src/config/api.js` | Axios instance with auto token refresh |

## Key Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Purpose |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `MONGO_URL` | `mongodb://localhost:27017` | MongoDB connection |
| `DB_NAME` | `ssh_runner_db` | Database name |
| `JWT_SECRET_KEY` | — | JWT signing key |
| `ENCRYPTION_KEY` | — | Fernet key for host credentials |
| `CORS_ORIGINS` | `*` | Allowed CORS origins |
| `SCHEDULER_POLL_SECONDS` | `30` | Scheduler interval |

## Default Credentials (dev)

- Admin: `admin` / `admin123` (created on first startup)

